{"tid":782911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【獨家】高鐵用不合格螺絲帽 逾萬粒疑藏車站恐致結構現裂痕","createTime":"2018-08-17T06:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T17:05:30.000Z","uid":30647,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"6260eb5e9cb4bd7db4583e3cb2b874804e505a7a","tid":782911,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:54:13.000Z","msg":"繼續爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>【獨家】高鐵用不合格螺絲帽 逾萬粒疑藏車站恐致結構現裂痕</strong><br />\n<br />\n港鐵沙中綫鋼筋和螺絲帽（Coupler）接連出現問題，《蘋果》獲悉，下月通車的廣深港高鐵，工程使用螺絲帽亦爆出不合格醜聞。屋宇署承認，調查發現螺絲帽拉力和延展測試均「肥佬」，曾停工四個月，棄用有關批次的螺絲帽，但部份批次超標螺絲帽仍留在石屎內無補救。<span style=\"color: red;\">署方稱不影響安全及耐用性，無嚴重違反《建築物條例》規定，最終「放生」有關人士，無做檢控或懲處。</span><br />\n<br />\n........................<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180817/58567980\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58567980&d=pA37NK4D6xUPDCHRwULZb8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6688da9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180817%2F58567980&h=a2f3499d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180817/58567980</a>"},{"pid":"11e33ea4efb9c83038fbfc004ff50daf5eae6bfa","tid":782911,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45c8613726fbc8ee2b6ed09f076d1443f51d65f","tid":782911,"uid":55597,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:00:40.000Z","msg":"希望快 D 通車之後陷橋"},{"pid":"2aec823dfa57246b9eb6648531bc9803997bd87c","tid":782911,"uid":79287,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"f45c8613726fbc8ee2b6ed09f076d1443f51d65f","tid":782911,"uid":55597,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:00:40.000Z","msg":"希